{"lemma":"عَجُولِ","slug":"عَجُولِ","root":"ع.ج.ل","root_slug":"ع-ج-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-ج-ل","pos":"ADJ","pos_camel":"adj","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"عَجُول","root":"عجل","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["adj","noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n28205","n28214"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B9%D9%8E%D8%AC%D9%8F%D9%88%D9%84%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"fast, quick"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"hasty, rash"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"plural of عِجْل (ʕijl)","tags":["form-of","plural"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Compare عَجِلَ (ʕajila, “to hurry, to rush”)."},"ipa":["/ʕa.d͡ʒuːl/","/ʕu.d͡ʒuːl/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n28205","headword_ar":"عَجُولٌ","root":"Ejl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EajilN","text_ar":"عَجِلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b2-  Also A she camel"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"distracted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"confounded,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"perplexed, having lost her young one;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K; *) because of her quickness in her motions, (K, TA,) i. e. in her coming and going, (TA,) by reason of impatience: (K, TA:) and a woman"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bereft of her child:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EujulN","text_ar":"عُجُلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O, K,) and, accord. to the K,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EajaAy^ilu","text_ar":"عَجَايِلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", but correctly ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maEaAjilu","text_ar":"مَعَاجِلُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", as in the L, an anomalous pl. (TA.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEajuwlu","text_ar":"العَجُولُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Death,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the decree of death;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Almaniy~apu","text_ar":"المَنِيَّةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (AA, K, TA:) because it [often] hurries him whom it befalls so as to prevent him from reaching his family. (TA.) ―         -b4-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Euj~aAlN","text_ar":"عُجَّالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and see a phrase in the latter half of the second paragraph of this art."}],"source_refs":["K","TA","O","AA"]},{"entry_id":"n28214","headword_ar":"عِجَّوْلٌ","root":"Ejl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see the next preceding paragraph, in two places.       -A2-  And see also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EijolN","text_ar":"عِجْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}